Program: Thinking Allowed
Title: Shoes
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/m00010yy
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 12 Nov 2018
Shoes: Laurie Taylor explores their cultural history and sociological meanings. He's joined by Elizabeth Semmelhack, Senior Curator of the Bata Shoe Museum in Toronto, Tim Edwards, Honorary Fellow in Sociology at the University of Leicester and Naomi Braithwaite, Senior Lecturer in the School of Art & Design at Nottingham Trent University. Producer: Jayne Egerton Show less